	Securities Authorized for Issuance under Equity Compensation Plans









	The information required by this item with respect to our equity compensation plans is incorporated by reference to our Proxy Statement for the 2017 Annual Meeting of Stockholders to be filed with the SEC within 120 days of the fiscal year ended


	December 31, 2016


	.









